Fixes: dc23103278c5 ("perf ftrace: Add support for -a and -C option")
Link: http://lkml.kernel.org/r/1564734592-15624-1-git-send-email-zhe.he@windriver.com
Signed-off-by: Arnaldo Carvalho de Melo <acme@redhat.com>
